highlights.text: “About You” by The 1975 has been on Viral Songs Indonesia the longest, at 408 days straight.
CORTIS has the most spots on Viral Songs Indonesia. “FaSHioN” is the highest at #1.
“Saxo Thailand - remix” by Dj Bouchenka and Anonyme Deejay is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Indonesia, up 15 spots at #63.
